\begin_layout Enumerate-Resume
Line 14.
 Suppose the standard deviation estimates are 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\vb{\sigma}}=(\hat{\sigma}_{1},\ldots,\hat{\sigma}_{p})^{T}$
\end_inset

.
 Create 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{u},$
\end_inset

